    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes the Internet X.509 Public Key Infrastructure (PKI) Certificate Management Protocol (CMP).  Protocol messages are defined for X.509v3 certificate creation and management.  CMP provides on-line interactions between PKI components, including an exchange between a Certification Authority (CA) and a client system. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
